EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN COALESCE( SCF_TCLS_LOANPASTDUE_1_0.UPDATE_TIME ,'') = '' THEN timestamp'1000-01-03 00:00:00.000GMT+7' ELSE to_timestamp( SCF_TCLS_LOANPASTDUE_1_0.UPDATE_TIME , 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS' ) END
CASE WHEN SCF_TCLS_LOANPASTDUE_1_0.PASTDUE_DATE IS NULL THEN DATE '1000-01-03' ELSE to_date(SUBSTR(CAST( SCF_TCLS_LOANPASTDUE_1_0.PASTDUE_DATE AS VARCHAR(26)),1,10), 'yyyy-MM-dd') END
